Nigerian superstar Wizkid met up with American rapper, P. Diddy in the US. The two superstars seemed to be having a swell time together as they shared a video on Instagram with Diddy raining praises of WIzkid, “This young black king, look at him. Touched down, and came to see the god.” Diddy said. Diddy also said he is coming back home. It is speculated that this home may be Nigeria but the rapper didn’t specify. “To be clear, you all know I’m coming back home. I’m coming back while I’m looking young and pretty too. I ain’t gonna wait too long.” STARBOY x Diddy! One Love. A post shared by  Wizkid News (@wizkidnews) on Jul 27, 2018 at 11:35am PDT 